==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superstruction
<hw>Su`per*struc"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of superstructing, or building upon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is superstructed, or built upon some
foundation; an edifice; a superstructure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My own profession hath taught me not to erect new
<qex>superstructions</qex> upon an old ruin.</q>
<rj><qau>Denham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superstructive</ent>⟦br⟧
